    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-80dc-8d8a-db2267eb9b72",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Open University has invested in early warning systems that flag and allow students at risk of failing the module. The paper goes over methods to analyze students in a VLE (Markov Chains and GUHA). While both are effective, Markov Chain analysis allows for the modelling of temporal dependencies.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
